Photo's of "Joleene Beaver" and "Kerry  
Beaver" - These are not real names but the photos are of my real friends  
and McHendry has no authorization to publish them.

The two photos on this blog of girls I know were taken by me at a  
festival... Peter McHendry the author of the blogs does not have my  
permission to use these images.

I made one complaint and then found another blog containing the same  
images...

Please take the photo's from the site (if you can take the whole site
down,  
I would appreciate that too)

Regards,

Joe
